verbose_text: PCR was performed in a 50 mul reaction mixture that consisted of template DNA (5muL), 10xPCR buffer (TaKaRa, Dalian, China), 1muM each of forward and reverse primers, 2mM MgCl 2, 100mM of each deoxynucleoside triphosphate (dNTP), and 1 unit of LA TaqTM DNA Polymerase (TaKaRa, Dalian, China).
